nodes.text: Fensi Moisk was a Kajain'sa'Nikto spacer who was active in the twilight years of the Galactic Republic. Moisk met the Aqualish Ix Bantagash and apparently they had a friendly relationship and was present in the Tatooinian spaceport of Mos Espa in 22 BBY, when Anakin Skywalker and Padmé Amidala came to see the local junk dealer named Watto.
